FullTitle: Amedei Presents The Cuisine of Chef Yves Schmid with the wines of Marchesi dè Frescobaldi
ShortTitle: Amedei Presents The Cuisine of Chef Yves Schmid with the wines of Marchesi dè Frescobaldi
FullDescription:
Date : 28 May 2015, Thursday
Time : 7pm
Price : $102.40++ (U.P.S$128.00++)
Venue : Senso Ristorante & Bar, 21 Club Street, Singapore 069410
Dress Code : Smart Casual

Delight your senses in a unique dining experience at Senso Ristorante & Bar, Indulge in a divine 5-course menu specially curated by Executive Chef Yves Schmid, each course gracefully presents the marriage of savoury and chocolate from Amedei. Look forward to a myriad of eclectic dishes exquisitely paired with the wines of Marchesi dè Frescobaldi.

FullTitle: Exquisite Parisian Dinner by Chef Pang with the wines of Gérard Bertrand
ShortTitle: Exquisite Parisian Dinner by Chef Pang with the wines of Gérard Bertrand
FullDescription:
Date : 26 May 2015, Tuesday
Time : 7pm
Price : $102.40++ (U.P.S$128.00++)
Venue : Antoinette, 30 Penhas Road, Singapore 208188
Dress Code : Smart Casual

Embrace in a Parisan evening and share Antoinette's joie de vivre in their beautiful surroundings reminiscent of an elegant boudoir with a range of meticulously crafted 7-course menu by Chef Pang. Diners can expect a line-up of tantalising dishes like Scallop Terrine with Prawn topped with Curried Crumble Butternut Squash and Crustacean Foam. Each course is exquisitely paired with the wines from Gérard Bertrand.
